4bk.title: Conjugacy classes of $S_5$
4bk.clickbait: The symmetric group on five elements is a group of just the right size to make a good example of a table of conjugacy classes.
4bk.text:
The [-497] $S_5$ on five generators has size $5! = 120$ (where the exclamation mark denotes the [-factorial] function).
By the result that [4bh in a symmetric group, conjugacy classes coincide with cycle types], we can list the conjugacy classes of $S_5$ easily.
